title: Bombay High Court dismisses plea over ‘Selfie’ song from Salman Khan’s ‘Bajrangi Bhaijaan’
text: The Bombay High Court today dismissed a public interest litigation seeking deletion of the famous 'Selfie' song from Salman Khan -starrer ' Bajrangi Bhaijaan ' as the actor is seen dancing with shoes before Lord Hanuman. »
